    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a convention for encapsulating Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) packets over the transport mechanism provided via the Internetwork Packet Exchange (IPX) protocol.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
